_:N0af1682e30ea48208bfb6ddacec972a7 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>If you are a member of the media and would like to speak to someone about the OIM and / or its work, please contact the CMA media team who are acting on behalf of the OIM.</p>\n\n<p>Journalists with enquiries can call the CMA’s press team between 9am to 5:30pm, Monday to Friday by:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>phone: 020 3738 6460</li>\n  <li>email: <a href=\"mailto:press@cma.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">press@cma.gov.uk</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you are not a member of the media, please contact the CMA general enquiries team by:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>phone: (020 3738 6000)</li>\n  <li>email: <a href=\"mailto:general.enquiries@cma.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">general.enquiries@cma.gov.uk</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
